    <h1 className="h1">Aescia helps clinical teams spot post-discharge risk earlier — without breaking workflows.</h1>

    <p className="sub">
      Structured patient check-ins, consistent escalation pathways, and a clinician-friendly view of who needs attention first.
      Built for real-world adoption: minimal friction, clear governance, and measurable outcomes.
    </p>

    <div className="ctaRow">
      <a className="btn btnPrimary" href="/contact">Talk to us about a trial</a>
